-9bd3-e4355191bf22": {"__data__": {"id_": "0c553e37-00d4-4af9-9bd3-e4355191bf22", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.unep.org/resources/emissions-gap-report-2022", "Author": "United Nations Environment Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Environment Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Emissions Gap Report 2022", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.unep.org/resources/emissions-gap-report-2022", "Author": "United Nations Environment Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Environment Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "b5408093bac5298cd81757f69a6adfc0e3f62cef66af0f5399bce9ac2084599c"}, "3": {"node_id": "7c06409e-51ca-4db0-bb23-59157b1e9ea8", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.unep.org/resources/emissions-gap-report-2022", "Author": "United Nations Environment Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Environment Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "4daf5bfe2c37406758cf2aef87a029a8ce73e2384116fd1fbeb10cfbafb895da"}}, "hash": "97757a2e19b2f14891c43c2525233f7d5ca779b292e6e74420f92ab673fa5477", "text": "and modified from Figure TS.25 from Pathak, M., Slade, R., Shukla, P.R., Skea, J., Pichs-Madruga, R., \u00dcrge-Vorsatz, D. et al. (2022). Technical summary. In Climate Change 2022: Mitigation of Climate Change. Contribution of Working Group III to the Sixth Assessment Report of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change. Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change. Geneva. https://www. ipcc.ch/report/ar6/wg3/downloads/report/IPCC_AR6_WGIII_TS.pdf. 0 Actual yearly flow compared to average annual needs (billion US$2015/year) Energy efficiency (IEA) Transport Electricity Agriculture, forestry and other land use 1000 1500 500 2000 Average flows (2017\u20132020) Annual mitigation investment needs (averaged until 2030) low low high high Multiplication factors Value GDP share Sector x2 x7 x7 x7 0 Act